Context("Numeric");

#given
$a = random(2,5,1);
$b = random(6,9,1);
$c = random(2,5,1);
$d = random(6,9,1);

#computation 
$Ans = .4*pi*($d-$c)*(cos($a)-cos($b));

#set tolerance
Context()->flags->set(
tolerance=>.01,
);

##############################################################
#
#  Text 
#
#

BEGIN_PGML

In free space, let [`\vec{H}=\frac{10^6}{\rho}sin(\phi)\hat{a_{\rho}}`] [`A/m`]. Calculate the flux crossing the surface defined by [`[$a]<\phi<[$b]`] and [`[$c]<z<[$d]`] [`m`].

[`\Phi=`] [_____]{"$Ans"} [`Wb`]  

END_PGML

